    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Cities Domination》是一款你需要建造各种中世纪建筑的游戏，每个建筑都有特定的功能。管理这些建筑之间的单位，收集食物、木材和石材等资源。使用这些资源建设更多的城市，扩展你的单位，制作工具、武器并训练士兵，派遣他们去敌方城市。建造并保卫你的城市，统治敌方城市，控制城堡以赢得游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抢先体验特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造最多10种建筑，扩展你在地图上的领土（将会添加更多建筑）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理单位和资源，决定哪些资源送到哪里。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集食物、木材和石材。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用所有资源确保单位的生存。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作工具和武器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >训练最多4种战士并攻击敌方城市（将会添加更多战士）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索最多25张程序生成的地图（将会添加更多地图）。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建设你的城市</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/5196421de0faae72534fc6b409b1a4b6.poster.avif?t=1761794078\" width=512 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/5196421de0faae72534fc6b409b1a4b6.webm?t=1761794078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/5196421de0faae72534fc6b409b1a4b6.mp4?t=1761794078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个建筑都有独特的功能，并需要必要的资源来建造。你需要选择你想要建造的城市来收集资源、制作武器或训练单位成为士兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理所有单位</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/36688538e60bbdfac4e82115b751f5f7.poster.avif?t=1761794078\" width=512 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/36688538e60bbdfac4e82115b751f5f7.webm?t=1761794078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/36688538e60bbdfac4e82115b751f5f7.mp4?t=1761794078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你有权在建筑之间分配单位，每个建筑将根据单位数量的不同而生产更多或更少的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>分配食物和资源</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/32703ed04db46caea028f8e17db67075.poster.avif?t=1761794078\" width=512 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/32703ed04db46caea028f8e17db67075.webm?t=1761794078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/32703ed04db46caea028f8e17db67075.mp4?t=1761794078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，每个单位每晚都会吃饭，你需要注意建筑和单位的食物量，以确保它们能够维持生存。如果某个单位无法进食，它们将离开城市。像单位一样，你可以在城市之间共享所有资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>攻击与防守</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/51e8414c4b61719a7e42bc183dd5bd15.poster.avif?t=1761794078\" width=512 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/51e8414c4b61719a7e42bc183dd5bd15.webm?t=1761794078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166610/extras/51e8414c4b61719a7e42bc183dd5bd15.mp4?t=1761794078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要攻击敌人的城市并征服城堡以赢得游戏！准备好你的军队，进行战略性攻击，并防御敌人对你城市的进攻。</p>",
